        </h1>
        <h2 class="mx-auto font-sans text-lg text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-100 md:text-xl md:leading-relaxed lg:w-2/3">
          I believe every problem presents an opportunity.<br />
          I'm a <strong>Customer Experience</strong> professional, specialized in B2B SaaS with a passion for people & technology.
          Currently helping secure the world's software @ <a class="text-primary-400" href="https://www.veracode.com"
            >Veracode</a
          >
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col space-y-2 pt-10 pb-16 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-center sm:space-y-0 sm:space-x-2"
      >
        <a
